{"title": "Blue Wound", "description": "On a search to answer the question \"Who started the Great War?\" the author details his encounter and subsequent journeys with a mysterious stranger - journeys not through towns and countries but through time. This spirit, whom the author names \"Mered,\" - meaning \"Rebellion\" - acts as a guide and interpreter of many epochs and episodes of human history, explaining how deep are the troubles that bring about conflict, from the interactions of two individuals to the mutual destruction of nations. - Summary by E. Sharp", "duration": 14403, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "19537", "name": "Garet Garrett"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/blue_wound_2602.jpg", "copyright_year": "1921", "genres": ["Horror & Supernatural Fiction", "Literary Fiction", "Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "E. Sharp"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "E. Sharp"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Christine Rottger"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "MrCrocodile"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Proemial", "readers": [11169], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/bluewound_00_garrett_64kb.mp3", "duration": 384}, {"section": 1, "title": "Ch. 1 - Mered", "readers": [11169], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/bluewound_01_garrett_64kb.mp3", "duration": 917}, {"section": 2, "title": "Ch. 2 - The Curse That Was", "readers": [11169], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/bluewound_02_garrett_64kb.mp3", "duration": 669}, {"section": 3, "title": "Ch. 3 - Urbanities", "readers": [11169], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/bluewound_03_garrett_64kb.mp3", "duration": 413}, {"section": 4, "title": "Ch. 4 - All East of Eden", "readers": [11169], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/thebluewound_2602_librivox/bluewound_04_garrett_64kb.mp3"